Scrolling in terminal (tty).
For scroll use Shift+PageUp, Shift+PageDown. When you switch between terminals tty, history buffer is clear.

Scrolling in screen util.
1. Ctrl+A, Esc
2. Use Arrow Up, Arrow Down for scroll
3. Esc or q for exit.
When you're scolling you can copy text. For this press Enter to start selection. When you finish selection press Enter again. To paste copied text use Ctrl+A, ]
